text: Auratote () is a location on South Uist in the Outer Hebrides, Scotland. Auratote is within the parish of South Uist. ==References== ==External links== *Canmore - South Uist, Cladh Choinnich site record *Canmore - South Uist, Beinn Ruigh Choinnich site record Category:Villages on South Uist
